<TEXT>
   the Democrats' chance of victory in the fall.
   ``Mike Dukakis is going to carry our party to victory in
November. He is going to win in the East, in the North, in the
West, and he is going to win right here in the South.''
   Bush, in a speech to the United States Jaycees in Richmond, Va.,
called illegal drugs ``the ultimate fatal attraction'' and
reiterated his call for requiring companies with government
contracts to have drug-free programs.
   ``The point is that stopping drugs in the workplace is not just
